api_list.description: This endpoint returns Random Dialogues of Superstar Rajinikanth.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://superstar.p.rapidapi.com/alpha/?format=json"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "superstar.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
